{"id": "1241972705972981801", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "雖然能第三應該是因為上午人少……另外我有點疑惑 上賽季的結算排名怎麼和賽季結束時候的不一樣 請問是什麼機制還是bug有人知道嗎", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T04:36:07.841000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
