{"id": "1241973525011763270", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "算了不找我的了，比如說榜一，上賽季看一直是女王之劍10000分，結算卻減半了", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T04:39:23.115000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤔", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
