{"id": "1241974159668678698", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "嗯……謝謝，希望會修復", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T04:41:54.429000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1241980057849692230", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "464292996263968778", "author_name": "danchaofan1529", "author_bot": false, "content": "没有啦没有要阴阳你什么，因为这个队确实不算好用，也像你说的会看操作习惯，那个组合几乎可以说是为我的手癖诞生的，所以昨晚看到镜像只是有种无法言喻的震惊(？)\n而且能和尤乌对局的机会本来就少，更何况还是镜像，也算是从别的角度审视了自己队伍的弱点，我觉得还挺好玩的<:shy:1239911338332127272>", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T05:05:20.665000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1241965800793837578"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1241971444485980181", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
