{"id": "1241991622229757962", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實挺好用的，我覺得你很有創意……不知道你記不記得昨晚，遇到你就輸，我換了汀克特淨化來反制也解不完出血+纏繞，還是輸了，然後就加入了\n不過今天遇到很多希洛水母隊，今天遇到女王之劍也是這個隊伍，基本穩定3-4回合一波速殺，出血流有點慢容易被克制，剛一看女王之劍還寫了攻略（我剛開始用discord）", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T05:51:17.828000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["464292996263968778"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1241980057849692230", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1241991699958464562", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "今天第一場也遇到油污了<:heart:1239910691218001961>", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T05:51:36.360000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1241991699744559124", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-20-13-50-18-09.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 161163, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1180850818509971466/1241991699744559124/Screenshot_2024-05-20-13-50-18-09.jpg?ex=6a377be8&is=6a362a68&hm=248dd3f23491d26802935d24279250f40f400f99f685910c310b77f9a7ebed31&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1241991786860384286", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "法洛思跟汀還是最少吧", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T05:51:57.079000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1241991908071309323", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "你的隊伍好新奇，法洛思後期有奇效吧", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T05:52:25.978000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1241991699958464562", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1241992197419831348", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "命輪是顛倒的，旋轉艾瑞卡十幾場只成功複製加固一次，這場甚至沒使用過<:flop:1236937860922343466>，反正就娛樂隊", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T05:53:34.964000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-20T05:59:10.339000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1241992321365704725", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "法洛斯是狂氣有奇效，有阿庫特很爽", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T05:54:04.515000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1241993715988561951", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "阿庫特+法洛思也很有創意，能解決命輪昂貴的缺點就好了……見到最多是給圖魯/24，不過24+專武幾乎是標配了", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T05:59:37.019000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1241996018724241489", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "464292996263968778", "author_name": "danchaofan1529", "author_bot": false, "content": "我倒是记得上赛季？还是什么时候，比较久远了，是不是你用汀和朵尔双净化，那局我才是真的一点办法都没有最后只好投降了<:flop:1236937860922343466> \n现在环境速攻爆破是很多，但otk队操作较为模板化所以更容易牵制，我用猫有个原因也是可以给otk队上状态(虽然要赌)。而且流血其实节奏可以很快，上面说的第二回合80+100血就是对阵女王剑的水母队，包括其他otk队遇到的时候也没有明显的劣势，除非发牌真得很烂不然大部分情况都还是能打的<:shy:1239911338332127272>", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:08:46.034000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1241965800793837578"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1241991622229757962", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242000158603083786", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "得知會修就放心了，謝謝你告訴我", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:25:13.058000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["464292996263968778"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1241980264222298256", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242000239091519559", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "我好像有點延遲，剛看見你的回復", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:25:32.248000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["464292996263968778"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1241996018724241489", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242000971345694851", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "那應該是上賽季……這賽季我沒用那個陣容了，那倒不是加入別人的陣容，是我自己搭的（這個少見），如果沒記錯那會兒是為了淨化應對越來越多的麻痺纏繞隊", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:28:26.831000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242001026270367785", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過也可能有別人在用", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:28:39.926000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242001407301783584", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "你汀是帶什麼命輪，我之前是帶遺忘之手", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:30:10.771000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242001513367474176", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "居然還有玩汀的🥹感動", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:30:36.059000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242001630501666888", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "我還試過用魔術師，玩隨機挺好玩的就是一直掉分……上賽季最後兩天我從3100+掉了1800多分，因為一直在試用稀奇古怪的陣容", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:31:03.986000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242001871997239337", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "我玩改後的流血隊也遇到過，魔術師+旋轉（這個上賽季我也有用），旋轉了驅散", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:32:01.563000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["464292996263968778"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1241996018724241489", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242002003165712415", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "464292996263968778", "author_name": "danchaofan1529", "author_bot": false, "content": "没我只见到你在用，因为环境里净化基本靠手杖，双净化很少很少，所以我印象蛮深的", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:32:32.836000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242002293830979594", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "464292996263968778", "author_name": "danchaofan1529", "author_bot": false, "content": "旋转驱散我也很头疼，因为缠绕也会被驱散掉完全没法<:flop:1236937860922343466> 只能开局速爆或者祈祷他别抽驱散", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:33:42.136000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242002346926542849", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "炒飯的流血隊還是強，我玩不來伽倫，速攻是受賜+血與沙了嗎", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:33:54.795000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["464292996263968778"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1241996018724241489", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242002611473874995", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "我之前有帶過臨界點（另外我環娜有時候也帶，我帶之前也沒見過別人帶這個，這個命輪比較冷門，後來就見到也有帶的了），還有帶過旋轉（為了轉淨化，但經常轉到3費遲緩……）", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:34:57.868000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242001407301783584", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242002768273735790", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "臨界點的易傷有時候奇效，環娜的打擊可以選目標，而汀的打擊貫穿", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:35:35.252000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242002830730989569", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "臨界點之前看到希洛有，我是朵爾/24帶過", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:35:50.143000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242003328175444039", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "464292996263968778", "author_name": "danchaofan1529", "author_bot": false, "content": "对的，还有那张幻影牌我忘记叫什么了，这三张配合可以在前三回合就秒掉/打残对面输出手。不过这也是发牌姬心情好的时候，实战如果开局牌一般我都会弃掉这些就是了", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:37:48.743000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1241965800793837578"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242002346926542849", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242003491602305065", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "那還挺開心的，因為奇特的陣容讓你記住……我印象裡遇到你還是輸多贏少，贏的時候一般是運氣好驅散多", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:38:27.707000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["464292996263968778"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242002003165712415", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242003991026470982", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "希洛的話我也見過，我是指那兩個角色，不過現在遇到希洛大部分是一波流了，剛我也去加入了一局希洛水母，結果不熟悉這個隊伍輸掉了", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:40:26.779000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242002830730989569", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242004262138155029", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "好像是血之悲歌，8出血？忘卻前夜的技能名一直挺詩意，看著賞心悅目", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:41:31.417000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["464292996263968778"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242003328175444039", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242004975312306218", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過玩汀克特的真的好少……對了，我嘗試奇特隊伍的時候也試過帶聚首時刻（為了複製淨化），結果慘遭卡手", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:44:21.451000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242001513367474176", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242005243043119105", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "24帶臨界點也很好用，用來配圖魯的麻痺隊嗎", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:45:25.283000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242006928444489739", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "464292996263968778", "author_name": "danchaofan1529", "author_bot": false, "content": "啊对对这张，我也觉得他们取名很贴角色，都很好听", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T06:52:07.114000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1241965800793837578"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242004262138155029", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
