{"id": "1242100297619214448", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家最近有沒有卡住？我遇到三次3000分的對手後就有兩次卡住，只能彈出，連抄牌也抄不了。", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T13:03:08.060000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242100792073130084", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@464292996263968778> 你怎麼帶了那麼奇怪的隊伍", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T13:05:05.947000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-20T13:05:16.609000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["464292996263968778"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242101009698787418", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是沒卡住，但我通常打兩場就下線了不準", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T13:05:57.833000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-20T13:06:37.958000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242101243950665728", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "原來你是至高之術，我對這ID有印像，上季有一次打贏你之後被你加入然後被你反殺<:flop:1236937860922343466>", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T13:06:53.683000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1241965800793837578"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1241971444485980181", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242102843582714017", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "464292996263968778", "author_name": "danchaofan1529", "author_bot": false, "content": "笑死原来是你，我本来在玩大福袋结果掉了一千分（……）然后就打算干脆玩下之前没玩过的，试队第一把就遇到你了，而且我刚刚还稀里糊涂地把顺序全搞反了进游戏才发现<:flop:1236937860922343466>", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T13:13:15.065000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242100792073130084", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242103217387474974", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "464292996263968778", "author_name": "danchaofan1529", "author_bot": false, "content": "没怎么排过詹金一下子想不起有什么队伍可以抄（不是）就组了个抽象队慢慢摸索", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T13:14:44.187000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242104112997208085", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "詹金前作是配拉蒙娜 <@611608223983599616> 或許懂", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T13:18:17.717000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["611608223983599616"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
